{"tid":2072705,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"天空體育：效力水晶宮的凱拉因心臟病去世，享年28歲","createTime":"2020-06-20T18:50:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-21T09:19:08.000Z","uid":92376,"like":8,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"3b448c375c77e6029e7c73524d07a75b70cbf20e","tid":2072705,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T18:50:40.000Z","msg":"據天空體育消息，水晶宮的吉祥物&mdash;&mdash;老鷹凱拉因心臟病發作去世，享年28歲。<br />\n<br />\n 近日，負責照顧北美禿鷹的鷹高地野生動物協會（EHWF)向天空體育證實凱拉已死於心臟病。<br />\n<br />\n EHWF透露，凱拉常年患有痛風，此前EHWF也曾試圖幫助她控制住病情。<br />\n<br />\n 此前EHWF向公眾籌集了4000英鎊來支付她的醫療費用，其中大部分都來自水晶宮的球迷。<br />\n<br />\n 2015年，凱拉正式成為球隊的吉祥物，此後每次球隊主場比賽前，她都會出現在塞爾赫斯特公園。 因此，她深受球迷和俱樂部的喜愛。<br />\n<br />\n 前水晶宮隊長告訴天空體育：&ldquo;球隊擁有凱拉作為吉祥物很開心，每次比賽前她都會讓你感到很驚奇，她讓每場比賽都變得與眾不同。我們會很想念她的。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://c2.hoopchina.com.cn/uploads/star/event/images/200620/badc3b5608f1fbf1cfe819db498cc1064c881537.jpg?x-oss-process=image/resize,w_800/format,webp\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc2.hoopchina.com.cn%2Fuploads%2Fstar%2Fevent%2Fimages%2F200620%2Fbadc3b5608f1fbf1cfe819db498cc1064c881537.jpg%3Fx-oss-process%3Dimage%2Fresize%2Cw_800%2Fformat%2Cwebp&h=796be0d2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d5f9991bd2cefc086c1a5ddcac7204e7349d8f2f","tid":2072705,"uid":8636,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T18:53:44.000Z","msg":"4000 鎊都要球迷夾？<br />\n球會唔包？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d6367f1943f4ed37b373aa93df72dd70d8f6cc3","tid":2072705,"uid":92376,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T18:53:54.000Z","msg":"RIP<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f4c96ad94b46acf16eb5e553649f8d726bdbd39","tid":2072705,"uid":297439,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T18:55:10.000Z","msg":"屌以為Martin Kel